oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Francis W. Strickland fireplace sketch
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Plate 72 of a collection of seventy-three original drawings belonging to William Strickland. The sketch shows detail of a fireplace, possibly designed for the Senate Room in the Tennessee State Capitol.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Strickland, Francis W.
